Simple Peer -  WebRTC (Video/Audio Calls) :
budo is development server based on browserify


var peer = new Peer({
	initiator: location.hash === '#init',
	trickle: false

})

By this we have initialized the peer which would be the initial peer
<pre> tag is used for indicating the preformatted text
